comment: I'm really impressed with this analyst's performance in high-volatility markets, with excellent accuracy! Highly recommend for anyone who likes short-term trading.
Overall performance is good, but the signals are sometimes unclear during low-volatility periods. Still an important tool in my investment portfolio.
Perfectly matches my trading style and helped me avoid several major pullbacks. The UI is also very intuitive and easy to understand.
It's a bit complex for beginners, but definitely provides valuable analysis. I wish there was a more detailed tutorial available.
I've been using this analyst for three months now, and the returns have been consistent. Great for investors who don't want to watch the market constantly.
Very precise guidance for short-term trading, although occasionally there are false breakout signals. Overall very satisfied.
Our team integrated this into our quantitative strategy, significantly improving the Sharpe ratio. Professional and efficient.
